room_title: Escape room "Espionage - A Candy Conspiracy" by The Great Escape of La Crosse in La Crosse
room_description:
Sweets N' Stuff is known as the worlds most secretive and eccentric candy company. They have recently announced their intention to begin production of a candy that will have the strength of steel, yet taste like whatever you want... simply by thinking about it!
â€‹Very few details are known publicly. You've been hired to make your way in and steal whatever information you can before production can begin. Under the guise of a one-hour shopping spree, you need to use your skills to find the top secret information and hand it over to your employer before the hour ends and you're caught with your hand in the cookie jar!
